Scanbuy,is,a,global,provider,of,mobile,barcode,solutions,that,make,use,of,camera,phones,The,ScanLife,solution,consists,of,a,multi,barcode,reader,application,with,millions,of,users,who,access,product,information,coupons,and,more,Scanbuy,offers,services,allowing,customers,to,create,integrated,D,barcode,solutions,The,ScanLife,API,allows,outside,websites,to,generate,codes,automatically,from,the,ScanLife,Code,Management,Platform,Interested,developers,should,contact,the,provider,for,more,information,about,the,API